descriptionNullable:
### Context

Call attention for how plastic may affect the physical processes in the oceans. And maybe suggest to Kaggle team a Machine Learning Classification Competition to reduce that impact on Marine life health and their physiology.

### Content

Images of Fish, Trash, Seabird eating trash and Seabird Carcass full of debris.


### Acknowledgements


Https://www.iflscience.com/plants-and-animals/seabirds-are-eating-plastic-litter-our-oceans-not-only-where-you-d-expect/ 

https://www.pewtrusts.org/pt/research-and-analysis/articles/2018/09/17/off-the-maine-coast-puffins-reveal-secrets-of-atlantic-herring-and-the-ocean

 https://www.indiatimes.com/trending/environment/11-heartbreaking-photos-show-plastic-waste-is-killing-birds-370258.html 

https://hakaimagazine.com/news/how-enough-floating-plastic-could-change-the-sea/

Photo by Ray Harrington on Unsplash


### Inspiration

Marine Life and their deaths linked to plastic ingestion.
title: Fish or Plastic? Birds/Plastic (Blastic) Deaths
subtitle: Attention to Seabirds' Plastic Ingestion.
